Mother.

14
00:03:28,485 --> 00:03:30,715
Her Majesty the Empress arrives!

15
00:03:39,094 --> 00:03:40,254
First Brother.

16
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:43,329
Your Majesty.

17
00:04:07,187 --> 00:04:08,449
So you are leaving.

18
00:04:10,457 --> 00:04:11,890
Are you afraid?

19
00:04:12,625 --> 00:04:14,183
You are my mother, Your Majesty.

20
00:04:16,862 --> 00:04:18,352
We have been
intimate for three years.

21
00:04:18,564 --> 00:04:20,657
You, of all people
should know who I am.

22
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:24,096
I am first and
foremost my father's son.

23
00:04:32,844 --> 00:04:34,004
Mother!

24
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,745
I am not your mother!

25
00:04:40,651 --> 00:04:42,846
Many things can be changed.

26
00:04:43,887 --> 00:04:46,219
In fact, nothing can be changed.

27
00:04:49,425 --> 00:04:51,086
Still, I would like to try.

28
00:04:52,728 --> 00:04:54,320
What are you going to do?

29
